        "description": "As of {{readr}} 2.0.0 (and the switch to {{vroom}}) both {{read_csv()}} and {{write_csv()}} allow the user to pass the number of threads to be used when processing (the {{num_threads}} argument). Currently this functionality is not exposed in Arrow. Some functionality (not yet the CSV read or write) allows the user to use the global CPU thread pool, but {{num_threads}} would offer more granular control. ",
